[08:46] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'is it first takes your prompt and it generates multiple images of your prompt to use as the first frame of the video and then for each image it would go ahead and generate a video clip and then it uses this reward model to basically'

[08:59] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'score each video clip based on its quality and then select the video with the highest score as your final video. So that\'s one algorithm. Another algorithm is called tree of frames'

[09:11] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'search. So again it takes in your prompt and generates multiple images from that as the starting frame of your video. It then goes through this reward component which basically eliminates any video'

[09:23] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
